{"tid":1111742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(真人真事）dllm 老鼠安差d累到我家變","createTime":"2019-04-17T04:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T10:44:12.000Z","uid":202351,"like":65,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"93660726ac72184d953ad3146eca2c9d30a9e2db","tid":1111742,"uid":202351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"尋日單新聞一出<br />\n我老婆已經係咁whatsapp 我<br />\nSend比我睇<br />\n我諗佢仲激動過鄭秀文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦 夜晚同佢一家食飯<br />\n佢一睇到電視播 又係度屌屌屌<br />\n之後佢突然間講<br />\n唔撚知邊條粉腸講過<br />\n呢個世界得2種男人<br />\n一種係會偷食既男人<br />\n一種係冇能力偷食既男人<br />\n戲肉黎啦<br />\n佢就問我外父係邊種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當時我心諗呢穫你仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知佢好撚淡定講左句<br />\n我都幾廿歲 唔搞呢d野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後突然間有6隻眼望住我<br />\n你呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後唔知邊度有把聲<br />\n答啦 仲唔答 答啦嘛<br />\nDllm d語氣完全同黑仔一鳩樣<br />\n我望住電視機 個腦一片空白<br />\n細細聲口upup 馬國明天放假一天<br />\n之後成餐飯大家一句野都冇講<br />\n到今日老婆都唔同我講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77481548c50e8ac88931d18b217608322cb3ddd8","tid":1111742,"uid":95637,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f82094669c50d80080d04d51502bd0795c1fd38","tid":1111742,"uid":40470,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文章內容充實富趣味<br />\n<br />\n9.5/10"},{"pid":"46264cbae4d4729d13eeab1fc29f0d22c5fa47e3","tid":1111742,"uid":202351,"